<section class="info-hero">
  <div class="container info-hero__inner">
    <span class="info-hero__kicker">Everything you need to know</span>
    <h1 class="info-hero__title">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1>
    <p class="info-hero__sub">UK, EU &amp; US orders ship with Evri. Easy 14-day returns. Questions? <a href="mailto:support@malowlondon.com" class="info-link">support@malowlondon.com</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section shipping-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="info-section__heading">Delivery</h2>
    <p class="info-body-text">We use <strong>Evri</strong> as our courier for the <strong>United Kingdom</strong>, <strong>European Union</strong> and <strong>United States</strong>. You'll receive a tracking link by email once your order has been dispatched.</p>

    <div class="shipping-cards shipping-cards--regions">
      <div class="shipping-card shipping-card--highlight">
        <div class="shipping-card__top"><span class="shipping-card__name">United Kingdom</span><span class="shipping-card__price">£2.99</span></div>
        <p class="shipping-card__time">1–3 days</p>
        <p class="shipping-card__desc">Estimated transit after dispatch (working days). Standard shipping <strong>£2.99</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="shipping-card">
        <div class="shipping-card__top"><span class="shipping-card__name">Northern Ireland</span><span class="shipping-card__price">£4.99</span></div>
        <p class="shipping-card__time">3–5 days</p>
        <p class="shipping-card__desc">Estimated transit after dispatch (working days). Standard shipping <strong>£4.99</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="shipping-card">
        <div class="shipping-card__top"><span class="shipping-card__name">European Union</span><span class="shipping-card__price">£7.99</span></div>
        <p class="shipping-card__time">5–8 days</p>
        <p class="shipping-card__desc">Estimated transit after dispatch (working days). Standard shipping <strong>£7.99</strong>. Duties and taxes may apply.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="shipping-card">
        <div class="shipping-card__top"><span class="shipping-card__name">United States</span><span class="shipping-card__price">£8.99</span></div>
        <p class="shipping-card__time">7–10 days</p>
        <p class="shipping-card__desc">Estimated transit after dispatch (working days). Standard shipping <strong>£8.99</strong>. Customs duties and taxes may apply.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-callout">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
      <p>Orders placed before 1pm GMT Monday–Friday are dispatched the same day where possible. Orders placed after this time or at weekends are dispatched the next working day.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section shipping-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="info-section__heading">Returns &amp; exchanges</h2>

    <div class="info-steps">
      <div class="info-step">
        <span class="info-step__number">01</span>
        <div class="info-step__content">
          <h3 class="info-step__title">Check eligibility</h3>
          <p class="info-step__desc">We accept returns within <strong>14 days</strong> of the delivery date. Items must be unworn, in original condition, and returned in their original box and packaging.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-step">
        <span class="info-step__number">02</span>
        <div class="info-step__content">
          <h3 class="info-step__title">Request a return</h3>
          <p class="info-step__desc">Email <a href="mailto:support@malowlondon.com" class="info-link">support@malowlondon.com</a> with your order number and reason for return. Our team will send you a tracked returns label within 1 working day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-step">
        <span class="info-step__number">03</span>
        <div class="info-step__content">
          <h3 class="info-step__title">Send it back</h3>
          <p class="info-step__desc">Pack your shoes securely and send the parcel using the tracked label we provide. Keep your proof of postage until your return is received.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-step">
        <span class="info-step__number">04</span>
        <div class="info-step__content">
          <h3 class="info-step__title">Refund or exchange</h3>
          <p class="info-step__desc">Once we receive your return, we'll process your refund or exchange within <strong>3–5 working days</strong>. Refunds are issued to your original payment method.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="info-section__subheading" style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:16px;">Return label charges</h3>
    <p class="info-body-text" style="margin-bottom:20px;">When you return an eligible order using our label, the following charges apply (free for faulty or incorrect items).</p>

    <div class="shipping-cards shipping-cards--regions">
      <div class="shipping-card shipping-card--highlight">
        <div class="shipping-card__top"><span class="shipping-card__name">United Kingdom</span><span class="shipping-card__price">£1.99</span></div>
        <p class="shipping-card__desc">Return label fee.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="shipping-card">
        <div class="shipping-card__top"><span class="shipping-card__name">Northern Ireland</span><span class="shipping-card__price">£3.99</span></div>
        <p class="shipping-card__desc">Return label fee.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="shipping-card">
        <div class="shipping-card__top"><span class="shipping-card__name">European Union</span><span class="shipping-card__price">£5.99</span></div>
        <p class="shipping-card__desc">Return label fee.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="shipping-card">
        <div class="shipping-card__top"><span class="shipping-card__name">United States</span><span class="shipping-card__price">£6.99</span></div>
        <p class="shipping-card__desc">Return label fee.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section shipping-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="info-section__heading">Faulty or incorrect items</h2>
    <p class="info-body-text">We take quality seriously. If you've received a faulty or incorrect item, please contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:support@malowlondon.com" class="info-link">support@malowlondon.com</a> with your order number and a photo of the issue. We'll arrange a free return and replacement (or full refund) as a priority.</p>
    <div class="info-cta-row">
      <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/contact" class="btn-rect">Contact us</a>
      <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/size-guide" class="btn-rect-ghost">Size guide</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

